Package soot.dexpler

Class DexMethod

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.dexpler.DexMethod
  • public class DexMethod
extends Object
    DexMethod is a container for all methods that are declared in a class. It holds information about its name, the class it belongs to, its access flags, thrown exceptions, the return type and parameter types as well as the encoded method itself.
